author: Discovery
description:
In the Eye of the Storm brings together the most jaw-dropping moments from across the series including twin tornadoes, monster hurricanes and blizzards that bury entire towns. Featuring real footage from fearless chasers and eyewitnesses, this compilation dives straight into nature’s chaos, where every storm tells a story and every second counts.

Stream Full Episodes of In the Eye of the Storm:
https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/in-the-eye-of-the-storm-us

#Discovery #IntheEyeoftheStorm

About In the Eye of the Storm:
This series reveals recent natural disasters as they happened in real-time through footage captured by eyewitnesses who found themselves in the wrong place at the right time and boldly held up their camera phones to capture the eye of the storm.

description:
Josh Gates dives into the mystery of Amelia Earhart’s disappearance by following her final flight route across the Pacific. He hunts for clues, talks to experts and explores islands to uncover what really happened to the world’s most famous pilot!
#ExpeditionUnknown

Stream Full Episodes of Expedition Unknown:
https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/expedition-unknown

#Discovery #ExpeditionUnknown

About Expedition Unknown: 
Josh Gates investigates the truth behind the world's most iconic and captivating legends. Leaving no stone unturned, his adventures take him around the globe as he immerses himself in the core locales linked to each tale.
